  </header>
  <div class="container">
    <div id="about-container">
      <h1 class="content-title">
        <span class="feature-description">About</span>
      </h1>
      <h3>pocketSOHO helps SMALL or HOME Business owners run their business</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <%= image_tag "landing/browser.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
      <img src="./img/masthead/browser.png" class="img-responsive" alt="Macbook">
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <ul class="icons-list">
            <li>
              <i class="icon-li fa fa-check text-primary"></i>
              Instant Message Customers
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="icon-li fa fa-check text-primary"></i>
              Schedule appointments
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="icon-li fa fa-check text-primary"></i>
              Send Invoices & Track Payments
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <ul class="icons-list">
            <li>
              <i class="icon-li fa fa-check text-primary"></i>
              Integrated & Secured Online Payment
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="icon-li fa fa-check text-primary"></i>
              Track & Visual Income
            </li>
            <li>
              <i class="icon-li fa fa-check text-primary"></i>
              Speed-up Tax Reporting
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
          <p>Easiest way of combining the most needed 3 features to run a small office, home office, individual service business such as piano teacher, therapist, tutor, yoga teacher, nanny, and dog walker.</p>
          <br/>
          <%= link_to "Start Your Free Trial", new_user_path, {id: 'info-btn3', class: 'btn btn-primary btn-jumbo'} %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br>

  </div>

</div>

